## âœ… How to Run Locally

```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/udaynandaniya/University_data_portal.git
cd University_data_portal

# Start backend
cd server
npm install
npm run dev

# Start frontend
cd ../client
npm install
npm start
````

